lead_paragraph: After Kevin Streelman opened the Sanderson Farms Championship with a 9-under 63 on Thursday, he and several other players said it would take 20 under or better to win.

headline.print_headline: Chris Kirk, Luke List Share PGA Tour Lead in Mississippi
